text: Kurgatovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Kurgatovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 278 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Kurgatovo
